block subSubTitle
	h1
		b Logistic function (AKA sigmoid, logit)
block subSubContent
	h3
		b The function
	p \(\sigma (z)=\frac{1}{1+e^{-z}}\)
	p The range of this activation is between \(0\) and \(1\).

	h3
		b The derivative
	p \(\sigma '(z)=\frac{e^{-z}}{(1+e^{-z})^2}\)
	p \(\sigma '(z)=\sigma (z)\frac{1+e^{-z}-1}{1+e^{-z}}\)
	p \(\sigma '(z)=\sigma (z)[1-\sigma (z)]\)
	h3
		b Notes
	p 
